WebServicesSection Class

Definition

Represents the webServices element in the configuration file. This element controls the settings of XML Web services.

In this Article

public sealed class WebServicesSection : System.Configuration.ConfigurationSection

ConformanceWarnings

Gets the collection of conformance warnings for the Web Service. This property corresponds to the configurationWarnings element in the configuration file.

public System.Web.Services.Configuration.WsiProfilesElementCollection ConformanceWarnings { get; }
Value
WsiProfilesElementCollection

A WsiProfilesElementCollection object that represents the collection of conformance warnings for the Web Service.

Current

public static System.Web.Services.Configuration.WebServicesSection Current { get; }
Value

A WebServicesSection object.

Diagnostics

Gets or sets the DiagnosticsElement for the WebServicesSection object.

public System.Web.Services.Configuration.DiagnosticsElement Diagnostics { get; set; }
Value
DiagnosticsElement

A DiagnosticsElement for the current configuration file.

EnabledProtocols

Gets one of the WebServiceProtocols values that indicates the Web service protocol.

public System.Web.Services.Configuration.WebServiceProtocols EnabledProtocols { get; }
Value
WebServiceProtocols

One of the WebServiceProtocols values.

protected override System.Configuration.ConfigurationPropertyCollection Properties { get; }
Value

To be added.

Protocols

Gets the transmission protocol that is used to decrypt data sent from a client browser in an HTTP request.

public System.Web.Services.Configuration.ProtocolElementCollection Protocols { get; }
Value
ProtocolElementCollection

A WebServiceProtocols object that represents the transmission protocol that is used to decrypt data sent from a client browser in an HTTP request.

Remarks

The data sent in an HTTP request to an XML Web service can contain method calls and parameters.

ServiceDescriptionFormatExtensionTypes

Gets the TypeElementCollection that specifies the service description format extension to run within the scope of the configuration file.

public System.Web.Services.Configuration.TypeElementCollection ServiceDescriptionFormatExtensionTypes { get; }
Value
TypeElementCollection

A TypeElementCollection that specifies the service description format extension to run within the scope of the configuration file.

SoapEnvelopeProcessing

Gets or sets the SoapEnvelopeProcessingElement for the WebServicesSection object.

public System.Web.Services.Configuration.SoapEnvelopeProcessingElement SoapEnvelopeProcessing { get; set; }
Value
SoapEnvelopeProcessingElement

A SoapEnvelopeProcessingElement for the current configuration file.

SoapExtensionImporterTypes

Gets the TypeElementCollection that specifies the SOAP extensions to run when a service description for an XML Web service within the scope of the configuration file is accessed.

public System.Web.Services.Configuration.TypeElementCollection SoapExtensionImporterTypes { get; }
Value
TypeElementCollection

A TypeElementCollection that specifies the SOAP extensions to run when a service description for an XML Web service within the scope of the configuration file is accessed.

SoapExtensionReflectorTypes

Gets the TypeElementCollection that specifies the SOAP extensions to run when a service description is generated for all XML Web services within the scope of the configuration file.

public System.Web.Services.Configuration.TypeElementCollection SoapExtensionReflectorTypes { get; }
Value
TypeElementCollection

A TypeElementCollection that specifies the SOAP extensions to run when a service description is generated for all XML Web services within the scope of the configuration file.

SoapExtensionTypes

Gets the SoapExtensionTypeElementCollection that specifies the SOAP extensions to run with all XML Web services within the scope of the configuration file.

public System.Web.Services.Configuration.SoapExtensionTypeElementCollection SoapExtensionTypes { get; }
Value
SoapExtensionTypeElementCollection

A SoapExtensionTypeElementCollection that specifies the SOAP extensions to run with all XML Web services within the scope of the configuration file.

SoapServerProtocolFactoryType

Gets a TypeElement object that corresponds to the protocol used to call the Web service.

public System.Web.Services.Configuration.TypeElement SoapServerProtocolFactoryType { get; }
Value
TypeElement

A TypeElement object that corresponds to the protocol used to call the Web service.

SoapTransportImporterTypes

Gets a TypeElementCollection object that represents the SoapTransportImporterTypes configuration element.

public System.Web.Services.Configuration.TypeElementCollection SoapTransportImporterTypes { get; }
Value
TypeElementCollection

A TypeElementCollection object that represents the SoapTransportImporterTypes configuration element.

WsdlHelpGenerator

Gets the Web service Help page (an .aspx file) that is displayed to a browser when the browser navigates directly to an ASMX page.

public System.Web.Services.Configuration.WsdlHelpGeneratorElement WsdlHelpGenerator { get; }
Value
WsdlHelpGeneratorElement

A WsdlHelpGeneratorElement object that specifies the XML Web service Help page (an .aspx file) that is displayed to a browser when the browser navigates directly to an ASMX XML Web service page.
